      <title>交易员认为大转折点即将到来，日元飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/yen-bets-grow-on-signs-tipping-point-for-us-japan-rates-is-near</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着人们越来越预期日本和美国之间的利差最终将缩小，日元出现拐点的迹象正在增多。]]></description>
