    <item>
      <title>人工智能抛售席卷全球，股市下跌，日元上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，欧洲股指期货与亚洲股市一同下跌，因为投资者开始撤出今年推动牛市的人工智能狂热。在下周日本央行会议召开之前，日元连续第四天上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 22:35:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易进展缓慢令投资者失望，麦格理股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/macquarie-says-commodities-and-markets-unit-sees-trading-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦格理集团有限公司 (Macquarie Group Ltd.) 股价出现五个多月来最大跌幅，原因是与美国的交易活动激增不同，澳大利亚的交易步伐似乎放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/macquarie-says-commodities-and-markets-unit-sees-trading-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 22:16:43 GMT</pubDate>
